import React from 'react';
import '../styles/logo.css'; // стили для анимации

function Logo() {
  return (
    <svg
      width="60"
      height="60"
      viewBox="0 0 64 64"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      role="img"
      aria-label="Picture Frame Icon"
      style={{ cursor: 'pointer' }}
    >
      {/* Рамка */}
      <rect
        x="5"
        y="5"
        width="54"
        height="54"
        rx="4"
        ry="4"
        fill="none"
        stroke="#6a4c93"
        strokeWidth="4"
      >
        <animate
          attributeName="stroke"
          values="#6a4c93;#9c8bc9;#6a4c93"
          dur="3s"
          repeatCount="indefinite"
        />
      </rect>

      {/* Картина — простая гора и солнце */}
      <polygon points="12,48 26,28 38,48" fill="#f4a261" />
      <circle cx="46" cy="22" r="7" fill="#e76f51" />
      <rect x="40" y="44" width="12" height="6" fill="#2a9d8f" />
    </svg>
  );
}

export default Logo;
